maybe I would've said they ain't.

02:19:59.058 --> 02:20:01.852
But now, it's all life is.

02:20:02.853 --> 02:20:05.147
Even if it lasts no time at all.

02:20:05.231 --> 02:20:07.692
A month, a day even.

02:20:08.276 --> 02:20:10.236
