02:20:12.113 --> 02:20:13.364
What's wrong?

02:20:14.323 --> 02:20:15.658
Chino...

02:20:16.242 --> 02:20:17.368
What?

02:20:18.035 --> 02:20:19.912
Chino has a gun.

02:20:22.123 --> 02:20:25.626
Chino shot Maria.

02:20:29.463 --> 02:20:31.215
