02:21:21.307 --> 02:21:22.892
Chino!

02:21:25.102 --> 02:21:26.896
I'm right here!

02:21:28.939 --> 02:21:30.524
(Tearfully) Chino!

02:21:31.108 --> 02:21:32.735
Chino!

02:21:34.070 --> 02:21:35.655
