02:22:31.669 --> 02:22:33.379
(Crying)

02:22:36.382 --> 02:22:38.718
Mi amor mio, mi corazon.

02:22:40.386 --> 02:22:41.679
(Softly) Maria.

02:22:42.680 --> 02:22:43.973
Maria.

02:22:44.390 --> 02:22:46.016
