02:22:53.649 --> 02:22:57.027
you're the only thing I'll see

02:22:57.486 --> 02:22:59.321
(voice quivers) Forever

02:23:00.614 --> 02:23:02.950
in my eyes, in my words

02:23:03.033 --> 02:23:05.411
