02:23:06.370 --> 02:23:08.372
(voice breaking)
Nothing else but you

02:23:09.415 --> 02:23:10.791
ever (sobbing)

02:23:11.292 --> 02:23:13.127
(Tony breathing heavily)

02:23:15.921 --> 02:23:17.214
