02:23:32.938 --> 02:23:35.024
(Maria continues sobbing)

02:23:55.920 --> 02:23:57.505
Give it to me.

02:23:57.588 --> 02:23:59.715
(Chino breathing shakily)

02:24:05.554 --> 02:24:07.348
