02:24:22.947 --> 02:24:23.948
And you?

02:24:26.033 --> 02:24:27.368
All of you!

02:24:28.911 --> 02:24:31.914
I can kill now because I hate now.

02:24:36.293 --> 02:24:37.837
I hate now.

02:24:41.382 --> 02:24:43.509
